ends of the market, nor, he averred, would it be commercially sensible to switch from one paper input to another on the same machine.{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s17{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af8\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af8\langfe255\hich\f8\fs20\lang1033\loch\f8\fs20\lang1033{\*\cs58\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f8\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 See page 270 of the transcript.}}}
