 As we will elaborate below, we accept that the vertically integrated firm is indeed a good business opportunity because it is, in essence, a mechanism for securing market domination.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af8\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af8\langfe255\hich\f8\fs24\lang1033\loch\f8\fs24\lang1033 
